George E. McFARLAND, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 21114. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. Oct. 29, 1965. George E. McFarland, in pro. per. Robert E. Hauberg, U. S. Atty., Jackson, Miss., for appellee.

Before JONES, WISDOM and GEWIN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM:

The record on this appeal does not disclose any prejudicial error. The judgment of the district court is

Affirmed.
